<b>Telebudget Bot</b>

Record your expenses and income with the Telebudget Bot.

List of available commands:

<b>Transaction Recording</b>
<code>/add /a</code> Record a new transaction

<code>/edit /a</code> Edit an existing transaction
<i>You need to reply related transaction chat first. You also could edit the past transaction chat directly</i>

<code>/delete /d</code> Delete an existing transaction
<i>You need to either reply related transaction chat first or provide a transaction id</i>

<b>Transaction Reporting</b>
<code>/sum</code> Summarize your transactions for a specific period or current month
